---
// src/pages/commercial/dishwasher-repair.astro
// Phase 3 Tier 2 (2026-04-28), neutral multi-county hub.
// title/H1/description/phone neutralized to 5 SoCal counties; Service schema with 5-county
// areaServed (was LocalBusiness with 8 LA cities); aggregateRating absent (already clean);
// Recent Repairs distributed 2 LA + 1 OC + 1 Ventura; Cities-served block → 5-county Counties block;
